text: I usually don't write bad reviews when the food is average but this just tasted really really bad. 4 of us ordered different bowls and all of them were definitely not fresh, intense spoiled taste and had to throw it away.
Service is very nice especially staff Narmatha suggestion the food her Service also nice

Good Kebabs At Reasonable Price.  Their kebaba are tasty and serving is just nice for a quick lunch.  Price reasonable at around $10 considering its in a generally expensive location for food.  Service is fast.  A ton of seats but can be crowded during peak lunch hours.  The “food truck” style adds a lot of charm.  Would be better if the serving is be a bit bigger.
Best chicken shawarma kebabs!!! Amazing and friendly service. Will come again to try other menu. Recomendeddd❣️❣️❣️

Great aesthetic vibes with truck, amazing service by the ladies, especially one of the staff there, I recalled her name is Nuraini. She’s very friendly and amazing. Very good service. The most important part is the kebabs and brownies are incredibly delicious. will definitely repeat again. recommended!
